            </h3>
            <p class="text-lg text-secondary-brand leading-relaxed">
              Provide essential information like mileage, condition, and any modifications to your muscle car.
            </p>
            {/* Arrow connector for desktop */}
            <div class="hidden md:block absolute top-12 -right-6 text-4xl text-accent/30">
